Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.ihuntwithjavalins.Player.Player

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Player>
    public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Player>
    This class represents a Player who competes to scan and own more valuable QRCodes than other Players in the application.
